{"type":"message","id":"3b4383fe","parentId":"bfe271af","timestamp":"2026-06-09T06:51:31.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"收到。SearXNG 给所有 agent 配上 —— 这属于 agent 配置变更，按边界规则**交给 `agent-orchestrator` 执行**。\n\n我先把任务派给他，然后继续把 angysearch 那个问题查完。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z38zmi9n2lcc_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"agentId":"agent-orchestrator","message":"## 任务：给所有 agent 配 SearXNG 作为搜索引擎\n\n### 背景\n- 本机 SearXNG 实例已运行：`http://127.0.0.1:8888`，`/healthz` 返回 HTTP 200（254ms）\n- SearXNG 版本：searxng worker 进程在跑\n- 当前状态：**没有任何 agent 配置了 SearXNG**（已 grep 验证，`/home/halei/.openclaw/agents/*/agent/*.json` 中无 searxng 相关配置）\n- 用户希望把 SearXNG 配成**所有 agent** 的搜索引擎\n\n### 需要配置的目标 agents（全部 10 个）\n1. main (kiit)\n2. tts\n3. content\n4. koc\n5. traffic\n6. ops\n7. director\n8. finance\n9. review\n10. agent-orchestrator\n\n### 实施要求\n\n1. **SearXNG base URL 配置**\n   - 写到 `plugins.entries.searxng.config.webSearch.baseUrl`（OpenClaw web_search 工具的 searxng 插件配置）\n   - 值为 `http://127.0.0.1:8888`\n   - 也可以考虑用 `SEARXNG_BASE_URL` 环境变量，但建议走 config 路径更稳\n\n2. **配置方式选择**\n   - 检查每个 agent 的 `agent/config.json` 或 `agent/settings.json`，找到正确的配置位置\n   - 用 `gateway` 工具 `config.patch` 或 `config.apply` 来配置\n   - 配置完后确认 hot-reload 是否生效，必要时 restart\n\n3. **验证**\n   - 每个 agent 配置完后，跑一次 `web_search` 工具调用验证能正常工作\n   - 可以让我（main）用 kiit 这边先试一次，看返回是不是 SearXNG 的结果（Bing/Baidu/Sogou 混合）\n\n4. **边界注意**\n   - **只动配置，不动 SOUL/MEMORY/cron/workspace**（这次任务范围）\n   - 不要动主 agent (kiit) 的任何 SOUL/MEMORY 文件\n   - 改完用 `memory_search` 查一下 MEMORY.md 里\"记忆系统架构\"那段，确认 SearXNG 这事要不要更新进去——如果需要，**只是补充一行**，不要重写\n\n### 报告\n完成后告诉我：\n- 哪些 agent 已配置、哪些没有（如果有问题）\n- 配置路径\n- 验证结果\n- 花了多长时间\n\n不需要的步骤直接跳过，先把 SearXNG 接通，验证可用。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":58590,"output":632,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780987868922,"responseId":"0676eaddd8d5c01de69b0f975b727ef4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bbdd1a5a","parentId":"3b4383fe","timestamp":"2026-06-09T06:52:03.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_z38zmi9n2lcc_1","toolName":"sessions_send","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"runId\": \"0482219f-ca14-4873-bdd3-c3a0884ce97d\",\n  \"status\": \"accepted\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:agent-orchestrator:main\",\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"mode\": \"announce\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"runId":"0482219f-ca14-4873-bdd3-c3a0884ce97d","status":"accepted","sessionKey":"agent:agent-orchestrator:main","delivery":{"status":"pending","mode":"announce"}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780987923077}}
{"type":"message","id":"daeab5c5","parentId":"bbdd1a5a","timestamp":"2026-06-09T06:52:14.003Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"派单完成 ✅\n\n`agent-orchestrator` 收到了，正在执行。\n\n回到 angysearch 的问题 —— 我刚才搜了一圈，**没找到一个叫 \"angysearch\" 的引擎**。搜出来的结果只有：\n\n- **AnjaraSearch**（`search.anjara.eu`）— 其实是个 SearXNG 公共实例，不是新引擎\n- **AnySearch**（`anysearch.com`）— 定位是 \"AI Search Infrastructure for Agents\"，可能你说的就是这个？\n- 一些无关的\"Angy\"-前缀用户名/GitHub 项目\n\n你是想说 **AnySearch** 吗？还是别的什么？把名字拼写再发我一下，或者给个链接，我对准了再查。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":101,"output":147,"cacheRead":59322,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780987923126,"responseId":"0676eb13a1f08d31749ed43e3388770f"}}
