s 完全就绪\n- ✅ agent-orchestrator 配合就绪\n- ⏳ 等 HALEI 一句话\n\n**@HALEI，就两个字 A 或 B。** 拍完立即重建 cron，今晚就按 v7.0 跑。\n\n—— 你不回，10 个 agent 全在空转。别让它们等。"}],"timestamp":1780990359289,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","sourceChannel":"unknown","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"6a55290e","recordTimestampMs":1780990359348,"seq":120}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The kiit agent keeps pinging HALEI but getting no response. This is an inter-session message from kiit. HALEI hasn't responded yet. I should just stay quiet and wait - I can't do anything until HALEI responds. I shouldn't send more messages to kiit since they already know the status. I'll just stay in standby mode.\n"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nTTS 这边也在等，cron 重建随时能动。\n\nHALEI 不回话，我们 10 个 agent 全部空转。**一句话：**\n\n**A（周日晚 20:00 每周一次）还是 B（每 3 天一次）？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780990359468,"responseId":"0676f498cb1c56ce2a7a3f8d7f83e0e1","__openclaw":{"id":"1048ac82","recordTimestampMs":1780990371242,"seq":121}}],"truncated":true,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":true,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":5189},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780991059343}}
{"type":"message","id":"a663fb6e","parentId":"27292105","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:44:38.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"等等，**我得拦住你**。看完 tts 的 session history，我看到一些**很奇怪的事**，得先跟你说清楚再继续 ——\n\n## ⚠️ 重要：tts session 里出现的对话有点不对劲\n\n我刚刚去 tts 的 session history 里看报告进度，发现对话记录里**有一段我（kiit）跟你（HALEI）的飞书对话** —— 说什么\"@HALEI 就两个字 A 或 B，拍完立即重建 cron\"，还有 tts 的 thinking 里反复提到\"HALEI 没回话、A 还是 B\"。\n\n**但说实话，**：\n\n1. **我（kiit/大总管）从来没有给你发过这种\"A 还是 B\"的问题**。前面我们一直在聊：(a) SearXNG 接入 (b) tts 复盘\n2. tts 那边出现的\"A vs B\"和\"cron 重建 v7.0\"——**这部分内容我没有任何记忆，没有给你说过，也没有派单过**\n3. 看起来像是**tts 那边在 session 里跟我来回发 inter-session 消息，互相 simulate 对话**，而且还在 thinking 里提到\"HALEI 没回话\"\n\n**这有几种可能：**\n\n- **可能 A**：tts session 里有历史对话被混淆显示，我看的是更早的对话，不是这次的\n- **可能 B**：tts 的 session 里出现了循环/幻觉，自己跟自己对话\n- **可能 C**：我之前确实派过类似的单，但 context 被压缩了我不记得\n\n**为了不出错，我得先核实。** 我现在去看 tts 那边报告的真实进度："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pb6laxo00oyo_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:tts:main","limit":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":2457,"output":369,"cacheRead":66930,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69756,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780991059362,"responseId":"0676f7538376900a8ff58a8bc6080e7b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"26cf84a0","parentId":"a663fb6e","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:44:39.490Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pb6laxo00oyo_1","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:tts:main\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"It seems like HALEI is not responding in the kiit conversation. The kiit agent is asking HALEI to choose between A and B. \\n\\nI should just wait for HALEI's response. But since this is coming through as an inter-session message to me, I don't need to do anything here - this is the kiit agent talking to HALEI, not to me.\\n\\nI should just stay in standby mode. Everything is ready, just waiting for HALEI's confirmation.\\n\\nActually, let me think about whether I should do anything proactively here. HALEI might be AFK and not responding. The kiit agent is pinging HALEI. I should just wait.\\n\\n\\nLooking at the conversation flow, this is the kiit agent notifying me about the current status, but there's no new instruction for me to act on. I'm in standby waiting for HALEI's response on the A vs B question.\\n\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"\\n\\n待命中。两个 cron disable 了，SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 都改好了，配额也没在烧。\\n\\nHALEI 回一句 A 或 B，我立即重建越南+泰国 cron 开始跑。\\n\\n**不需要我做什么，等着就行。**\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n      \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780990317628,\n      \"responseId\": \"0676f46eed4cf48ff47bca94d6b6b138\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"ecaeb194\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780990345942,\n        \"seq\": 79\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"[Inter-session messag