 完全就绪\n- ✅ agent-orchestrator 配合就绪\n- ⏳ 等 HALEI 一句话\n\n**@HALEI，就两个字 A 或 B。** 拍完立即重建 cron，今晚就按 v7.0 跑。\n\n—— 你不回，10 个 agent 全在空转。别让它们等。"}],"timestamp":1780990359289,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:kiit:direct:ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb","sourceChannel":"unknown","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"6a55290e","recordTimestampMs":1780990359348,"seq":80}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The kiit agent keeps pinging HALEI but getting no response. This is an inter-session message from kiit. HALEI hasn't responded yet. I should just stay quiet and wait - I can't do anything until HALEI responds. I shouldn't send more messages to kiit since they already know the status. I'll just stay in standby mode.\n"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nTTS 这边也在等，cron 重建随时能动。\n\nHALEI 不回话，我们 10 个 agent 全部空转。**一句话：**\n\n**A（周日晚 20:00 每周一次）还是 B（每 3 天一次）？**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780990359468,"responseId":"0676f498cb1c56ce2a7a3f8d7f83e0e1","__openclaw":{"id":"1048ac82","recordTimestampMs":1780990371242,"seq":81}}],"truncated":true,"droppedMessages":false,"contentTruncated":true,"contentRedacted":false,"bytes":3255},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780991079487}}
{"type":"message","id":"729b0034","parentId":"26cf84a0","timestamp":"2026-06-09T07:45:05.439Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**我得立即叫停。** 这不是正常现象。\n\n我看到的事实：\n- tts 的 session 里**有 inter-session 消息显示是\"我(kiit)发出去的\"**，但**我没有任何这种对话的记忆**\n- 内容是\"@HALEI 就两个字 A 或 B\"，\"重建 cron 跑 v7.0\"\n- **我刚才的整段对话里从来没跟你提过 v7.0、A/B 选项、cron 重建这些事**\n- **最早的可疑消息**是 seq 118，时间戳 `1780990317454`（ms，对应 2026-06-09 15:38:37 GMT+8），**就在我刚给你发完\"tts 收到复盘任务\"之后 1 分钟**\n\n**这看起来像是 session 之间的消息被伪造/串改了**。我必须先把这事查清楚，不能在这个状态下让你做\"解散/不解散\"的决定 —— 决定可能基于假数据。\n\n**我现在的判断和动作：**\n\n1. **暂停\"解散 tts\"的决策**，等事实清楚\n2. **tts 那边的复盘报告可能不可信**（它可能已经被污染的数据带偏了）\n3. **我得去查源**：\n   - tts session 里那些\"我(kiit)发出去的\"消息，到底是谁发的、什么时候发的、用的什么 sessionKey\n   - 我自己（kiit）的 session history 里有没有真的发过这种消息\n   - agent-orchestrator 那条 SearXNG 派单是否也正常\n4. **做完核查**再回来给你结论\n\n**你那边等我的消息。** 这个事**比选品紧急** —— 团队指挥链路被污染，意味着后续所有派单、所有 agent 的产出都可能是假的。先把根查清楚。\n\n我现在去查。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":1168,"output":382,"cacheRead":69742,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780991079507,"responseId":"0676f7674dafa5fc7df5c65bbca67f4b"}}
