{"type":"message","id":"71ae9518","parentId":"c1080809","timestamp":"2026-06-09T08:07:25.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**找到 4 个值得看的开源项目，2 个高度相关，2 个一般：**\n\n### 🟢 高度相关（直接用）\n\n| 项目 | 干什么的 | 链接 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **LifelongLazyLearner/qu-ai-wei** | **去 AI 味**，专做简体中文，专门有 `install-skill.sh` 可以装到 OpenClaw | https://github.com/LifelongLazyLearner/qu-ai-wei |\n| **MrGeDiao/shuorenhua（说人话）** | Chinese-first AI writing，直接按 SKILL.md 规则改写 | https://github.com/MrGeDiao/shuorenhua |\n\n### 🟡 可以参考\n\n| 项目 | 干什么的 | 链接 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **hylarucoder/ai-flavor-remover** | 推理模型上跑的\"AI 味去除 prompt\" | https://github.com/hylarucoder/ai-flavor-remover |\n| **pepper-hub/AIMedia** | 抓热点 + AI 生成自媒体内容（Django + PySide6 全套） | https://github.com/pepper-hub/AIMedia |\n\n### ⚠️ 关键发现\n\n> CSDN 博客原文提到：**\"在终端中执行 `clawhub install avoid-ai-writing` 一键获取完整项目代码\"**\n\n**也就是说 OpenClaw 有自己的 skill 商店叫 clawhub**，你说的\"3 个 skill 搞定\"可能直接就有。让我先查一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gd5ustm35yj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -sS \"http://localhost:8888/search?q=clawhub+openclaw+%E8%87%AA%E5%AA%92%E4%BD%93+skill+%E5%9B%BE%E6%96%87+%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9&format=json\" -H \"Accept: application/json\" 2>&1 | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nfor r in d.get('results', [])[:8]:\n    print(r['title'])\n    print('  ', r['url'])\n    print('  ', r['content'][:200])\n    print()\n\" 2>&1 | head -50","timeout":15}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gd5ustm35yj_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which clawhub; clawhub --help 2>&1 | head -20; echo \"---\"; clawhub list 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":3228,"output":569,"cacheRead":71577,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75374,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780992424123,"responseId":"0676fca83df0ec228b3ba7a81dd170f4